  "body": "There are no exact steps to reproduce this issue, and it occurs very rarely. So, the steps are not precise. Hope the logs might provide info what's happening\r\n\r\n### Steps:\r\n1. `User A` sends the CR to `User B`\r\n2. `User B` accepts the CR (Now `User A` sees the toast that his CR is accepted)\r\n3. `User A` sends any message into 1-1 chat\r\n4. `User A` waits 2-4 minutes\r\n\r\n### Actual result:\r\n1. `User A` sees the toast again that his CR is accepted (sometimes more than 4 times)\r\n2. `User A` the system message `<User B> now is a contact` is shown twice  (sometimes more than 4 times)\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/4b7acb54-7dc2-4553-9ffb-5e40789657fe)\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\nThe CR acceptance is shown only once\r\n\r\n### Logs:\r\n\r\n[Status-debug-logs.zip](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/files/12713593/Status-debug-logs.zip)\r\n\r\n### ENV: [Nightly: 25 Sep 2023]",
